# copas
# I had to invent most of these tournaments and resurect the Copa Mexico
# I had to do this because Concacaf does not have enough competitions (Or competitors) 
# to recreate a real environment, so for practical purposes with the Exception of the Libertadores Cup
# of which Mexico is an official participant I had to invent Concacaf-Conmebol competitions 
# details follow:
# Copa Libertadores de America (Needs no introduction)
# Copa de Campeones Conmebol - Concacaf (Those who win the national cups participate)
# Torneo de Copa Intercontinental (Those ranked 2nd to 4th in league 1 part.)
# Torneo de Copa Mexico (National cup, every team part.)
# Copa Interligas (National cup, teams from the first 4 leagues participate)
# Supercopa Mexicana (National supercup between the Primera Division Champ and Copa Mexico winner)
# Supercopa de Campeones Conmebol-Concacaf ( Copa Libertadores against Copa Interligas winner)
# Torneo de Ascenso (Teams ranked 4th to 8th play to find out who gets promoted)
Copa Libertadores de America 
Copa de Campeones Conmebol - Concacaf
Torneo de Copa Intercontinental
Torneo de Copa Mexico
Copa Interligas
Supercopa Mexicana
Copa de Campeones CONCACAF
Torneo de Ascenso


